{"tid":2409679,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得公廁黎講 蹲廁好過坐廁？","createTime":"2021-02-16T04:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T04:20:56.000Z","uid":15623,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5730ffd7a253de6a28fa767f275529a4478d19f3","tid":2409679,"uid":15623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T04:20:56.000Z","msg":"先唔講頂級公廁（朗豪坊戈堆）<br />\n<br />\n平時出面街市公園戈堆，污糟到仆街，成個廁板都係屎尿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要冇提供廁板紙/消毒液，靠紙巾根本唔會整得乾淨<br />\n<br />\n蹲廁起碼解決左呢個煩惱，但壞處就係要痞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總括而言我覺得除非個廁所本身有返咁上下水準，如果唔係用蹲廁仲好<br />\n<br />\n示意片：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ppm_Y8qdnKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fppm_Y8qdnKs&d=MttQmdgsIlWEqebbSf64%2BuvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=9ec2146d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ppm_Y8qdnKs</a>"}]}